Title: df: Add level for decreasing disk usage
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1625652695
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1


It is now possible to configure
thresholds in the rulesets 'Filesystems (used space and growth)'
to detect negative disk usage trends (e.g. loss of data).
